description: Hamas says it has chosen its local leader in Gaza to take over as the Palestinian militant group's new top political leader worldwide, following last week's assassination of the previous leader in Iran.
title: Hamas names Oct. 7 mastermind Yahya Sinwar as its new top leader

description: Three years ago, a group of young musicians from Afghanistan and their teachers fled Kabul to remake their lives as a community in northern Portugal. Now, they are touring the U.S.
title: Young Afghan musicians are rebuilding their art together, in Portugal

description: Supporters hope the chair of the Democratic Governors Association, ex-Army National Guard leader, former teacher and congressman can help Harris pick up support in the Midwest.
title: Harris taps Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz as her running mate

description: Debby is expected to bring up to 25 inches of rain across parts of the Southeast, the National Hurricane Center has said.
title: Tropical storm Debby is moving through coastal Georgia

description: A federal judge rules that Google illegally abused its monopoly power to maintain its control over the search engine business. Google says it’s appealing.
title: Google is defiant after losing antitrust lawsuit and being called a 'monopolist'
